<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .verify-link {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .verify-link a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .verify-link a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Reset password</h1>
        <p>Dear {{email}},</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password. If you did not make this request, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>To reset your password, please click the button below:</p>
        <p class="verify-link"><a href="{{link}}">Reset password</a></p>
        <p>This will expire in 15 minutes for security reasons.</p>
        <p>Regards,<br> The Monkey Team</p>
    </div>

</body>

</html>